	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false) ~> CovidADLS
CovidADLS select(mapColumn(
		date,
		all = World,
		poland = Poland,
		italy = Italy
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> SelectAndRename
SelectAndRename filter(date > toDate('2020-08-01') && date <= toDate('2020-08-31')) ~> OnlyAugust
OnlyAugust derive(dayOfWeek = dayOfWeek(date) ) ~> DerivedColumn1
DerivedColumn1 aggregate(groupBy(dayOfWeek),
	sumAll = sum(all),
		sumPL = sum(poland),
		sumIT = sum(italy)) ~> Aggregate1
Aggregate1 alterRow(upsertIf(true())) ~> UpsertIfTrue
UpsertIfTrue sink(input(
		dayOfWeek as integer,
		sumAll as long,
		sumPL as long,
		sumIT as long
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: false,
	validateSchema: false,
	deletable:false,
	insertable:false,
	updateable:false,
	upsertable:true,
	keys:['dayOfWeek','sumPL'],
	format: 'table') ~> SinkToSQLDb
